  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add diced red bell pepper and green onions, cook for an additional 3-4 minutes until softened slightly.",
    "Stir in cornstarch mixed with a pinch of italian herbs to create a paste. Cook for 1 minute until smooth and thickened.",
    "Mix in low-fat soy sauce and lemon juice, cook another minute to combine flavors.",
    "Fold in chopped parsley and serve hot as a side dish or over rice."
